sing specific cell references or coordinates, you should use the Range property correctly. Here's how to use Worksheet.Range and Worksheet.Cells properly with the .Merge method:

Correct Usage
To merge a range of cells, you can use Range.FromLTRB or specify the range directly using cell notation.

Example Code
Here's an example of how you can modify the header styles and merge cells using Worksheet.Cells and Worksheet.Range:

csharp
코드 복사
using DevExpress.Spreadsheet;
using System.Drawing;

// Assume 'excel1' is your SpreadsheetControl instance
Worksheet sheet = excel1.Document.Worksheets[0];

// Create a style for the header
CellStyle headerStyle = sheet.Workbook.Styles.Add("HeaderStyle");
headerStyle.Fill.BackgroundColor = Color.LightBlue; // Adjust color as needed
headerStyle.Font.Bold = true;                        // Make the font bold
headerStyle.Alignment.Horizontal = SpreadsheetHorizontalAlignment.Center;

// Apply the style to the first row (headers)
Range headerRow = sheet.Rows[0];
headerRow.Style = headerStyle;

// Example column merging logic (merging columns 2 and 3 in the first row)
for (int colIndex = 0; colIndex < 10; colIndex++) // Adjust '10' to the desired number of columns
{
    int startColumn = colIndex * 2;
    int endColumn = startColumn + 1;

    if (endColumn < sheet.Columns.LastUsedIndex + 1)
    {
        Range rangeToMerge = sheet.Range.FromLTRB(startColumn, 0, endColumn, 0);
        rangeToMerge.Merge();
    }
}

// Optional: Adjust column widths to fit the content
sheet.Columns.AutoFit(0, sheet.Columns.LastUsedIndex);
Explanation:
Define a Header Style:
Add a custom style to the workbook for header cells.
Apply color, bold font, and horizontal alignment.
Apply the Style to the Header Row:
Use Range to select and apply the style to the entire first row.
Merge Columns Logic:
Loop through columns in pairs and merge them using Range.FromLTRB.
Ensure that the merging range does not exceed the used column index.
Correct Use of .Merge Method
Alternatively, if you want to merge a specific range by directly using Worksheet.Cells, follow this approach:

csharp
코드 복사
// Merge two specific cells into a range
sheet.Range[sheet.Cells[0, 2], sheet.Cells[0, 3]].Merge();
Adjustments:
Adjust Color.LightBlue to your desired header color.
Modify the merging logic according to your merging requirements.
